            "title": "Consumer perceptions and reported wild and domestic meat and fish consumption behavior during the Ebola epidemic in Guinea, West Africa",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Lucie",
                    "lastName": "Duonamou"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
